text Route_201_EventScript_Boy_Text
{
    "Wild Pokemon lurk in tall grass. They\n"
    "can come bursting out at any time.\p"
    "So, if you're wanting to battle wild\n"
    "Pokemon, just walk in tall grass.\p"
    "If you want to avoid wild Pokemon\n"
    "then stay out of tall grass."
}

text Route_201_EventScript_Trainer_Tips_Text
{
    "Trainer Tips\p"
    "Don't be shy! Talk to anyone and\n"
    "everyone you happen to see.\p"
    "By talking to people, you will get\n"
    "invalueable information and advice."
}

text Route_201_EventScript_Girl_Text
{
    "If your Pokemon's health--that's its\n"
    "HP--is getting low, you should go\l"
    "home and get some rest."
}

text Route_201_EventScript_Mart_Guy_Give_Potion_Text
{
    "Hi!\n"
    "I work at a Pokemon Mart.\p"
    "Did you know that a Pokemon's health\n"
    "is measured by Hit Points (HP)?\p"
    "If a Pokemon Runs out of HP, it\n"
    "faints and can't battle anymore.\p"
    "If a Pokemon's HP gets low, you\n"
    "should heal it with a Potion.\p"
    "Here, let me give you a Potion as\n"
    "a free sample. First one's free!\p"
    "It will automatically go in the\n"
    "Medicine Pocket of your Bag."
}

text Route201_EventScript_Mart_Guy_Already_Gave_Potion_Text
{
    "You can find a Pokemon mart in cities\n"
    "and most major towns."
}

